void subscribe ( NotificationCenter &  notificationCenter)
override

subscribe to signal.

This function subscribes the signal localDomainInit,SystemShutdown ,TimingInit,DisturbanceEvent,and TimingStep using the function onLocalDomainInit,onSystemShutDown,onTimingInit ,onDisturbanceEvent,and onTimingStep respectively. The values are passed and assigned here
